title: Manchester United - The Double Champions. Season Review 2007-200
description:
Celebrate Manchester United&#039;s fantastic double glory with this must-have DVD - the official 2007/08 Season Review. Showcasing another agonisingly close-fought season, the DVD is packed full of action, with sensational strikes, last-gasp finishes, celebrations and highlights from every single game United played this season. Re-live all the action as Manchester United demonstrate their appetite for winning, achieving their 10th Premier League trophy!


Don&#039;t miss United as they make their mark on the Champions League. Highlights of their incredible European journey plus the drama and celebrations from the unforgettable final showdown with Chelsea, are united here. Forty years after first winning the European Cup at Wembley in 1968, the Reds are crowned the Kings of Europe again! Following a nail-biting shoot-out the Reds lifted their third European Cup, the second for Alex Ferguson during his 21 years at the club. The win made even more poignant by Club Captain Giggs&#039; performance breaking Sir Bobby Charlton&#039;s record of 758 appearances for Manchester United before collecting the trophy.


Watch this season&#039;s newcomers Anderson, Nani and Hargreaves make invaluable contributions to the team. Delight in the outstanding class displayed by Rooney and Tevez as they continue to forge a lethally effective partnership. And what more can be said about Ronaldo? Re-live his many breathtaking performances in what is another Footballer of the Year winning season for him. Score a winning result with this compilation, the definitive guide to another emotionally-charged season for the Reds.
